1
00:00:10,633 --> 00:00:13,367
<i> Bobby, I miss my mom so much.</i>

2
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:14,733
<i> Sorry.</i>

3
00:00:14,867 --> 00:00:17,367
<i>Let me handle the conversation
with Roman.</i>

4
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:18,333
<i> Godfather!</i>

5
00:00:18,467 --> 00:00:19,700
<i>Her flight to Hong Kong
is today.</i>

6
00:00:19,833 --> 00:00:22,100
<i>It's been almost four hours,
I can't contact Reign.</i>

7
00:00:22,233 --> 00:00:23,033
<i> I'll send you a link.</i>

8
00:00:23,167 --> 00:00:24,000
<i> What is this?</i>

9
00:00:24,133 --> 00:00:25,100
<i>I put a tracker on someone
earlier.</i>

10
00:00:25,233 --> 00:00:28,000
<i>Attorney, I'm sorry.
I didn't see you.</i>

11
00:00:28,133 --> 00:00:30,567
<i>They're going to the safehouse
to talk to Selena.</i>

12
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:31,300
<i> Who are these people?</i>

13
00:00:32,667 --> 00:00:35,100
<i>Ma'am, can I see the ticket
first?</i>

14
00:00:35,267 --> 00:00:36,900
<i>Well, that's the thing,
it's still in the office.</i>

15
00:00:37,033 --> 00:00:37,900
<i> So, let's go?</i>

16
00:00:38,033 --> 00:00:39,267
<i>Call our contact
in the traffic team.</i>

17
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:40,900
<i>Tell them to trace this vehicle.</i>

18
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:44,000
<i> Don't be so stubborn!</i>

19
00:00:44,133 --> 00:00:45,100
<i>- Come on!
- Help me!</i>

20
00:00:45,233 --> 00:00:45,900
<i> Selena!</i>

21
00:00:46,033 --> 00:00:46,633
<i> Get in!</i>

22
00:00:49,467 --> 00:00:50,400
<i> Dizon, let's go!</i>

23
00:00:50,533 --> 00:00:51,467
<i>- Sir!
- Enriquez!</i>

24
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,267
<i> What are you doing here?</i>

25
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:53,633
<i>Sir, my godsister was kidnapped.</i>

26
00:00:53,767 --> 00:00:56,000
<i>I had Noble trace the van.
He said she was brought here.</i>

27
00:00:56,133 --> 00:00:57,467
<i>Selena was kidnapped
from the safehouse.</i>

28
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,333
<i> She was brought here, too.</i>

29
00:00:58,467 --> 00:00:59,433
<i> Let me go.</i>

30
00:00:59,567 --> 00:01:01,567
<i>I promise I won't say anything
against Amo.</i>

31
00:01:01,700 --> 00:01:02,600
<i> You're annoying!</i>

32
00:01:02,733 --> 00:01:04,900
<i>You can't get away.
Do you understand?</i>

33
00:01:05,033 --> 00:01:06,933
<i> Have mercy.</i>

34
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:07,933
<i> It's Reign!</i>

35
00:01:08,067 --> 00:01:09,067
<i> Enriquez, wait.</i>

36
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,033
<i> Get them ready.</i>

37
00:01:10,167 --> 00:01:11,833
<i>Later, we'll take them
somewhere.</i>

38
00:01:11,967 --> 00:01:13,133
<i> Come on!</i>

39
00:01:13,267 --> 00:01:14,000
<i> Hey!</i>

40
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,433
Bring them here.

41
00:01:21,467 --> 00:01:21,967
Hey!

42
00:01:26,833 --> 00:01:28,867
- Boss, we've been followed.
- Go check on them.

43
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,800
Yes, Boss.

44
00:01:29,933 --> 00:01:31,433
Come here, come here!

45
00:01:31,567 --> 00:01:32,933
Let's go to the helicopter,
quick!

46
00:01:33,067 --> 00:01:35,300
Where are you taking us?

47
00:02:28,233 --> 00:02:29,000
Let's go!

48
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,400
Dizon!

49
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,233
Hurry up!

50
00:03:36,433 --> 00:03:37,533
Come here!

51
00:03:37,667 --> 00:03:38,400
Faster!

52
00:03:41,233 --> 00:03:41,900
Hurry.

53
00:03:50,633 --> 00:03:53,733
Enriquez, there they are!
Let's go!

54
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:54,567
Let's go!

55
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,167
Damn it!

56
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,833
It looks like someone
followed Conde.

57
00:04:11,967 --> 00:04:13,067
I was talking to him earlier...

58
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:15,867
but the line was choppy.

59
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,100
All I understood was...

60
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,433
compound and...

61
00:04:21,667 --> 00:04:22,700
and highway.

62
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:23,967
Compound, Chief?

63
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:25,033
Why?

64
00:04:25,167 --> 00:04:26,500
Do you know something, Noble?

65
00:04:26,633 --> 00:04:30,133
Sergeant Enriquez asked me
to help her find a van earlier.

66
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:32,233
It looks like someone she knows

67
00:04:32,367 --> 00:04:33,500
is a victim of human
trafficking.

68
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:37,000
The van was spotted
at a compound on Lamar Highway.

69
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:56,767
Hey!

70
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:57,400
Hide!

71
00:05:11,833 --> 00:05:13,300
Where's the helicopter going?

72
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,500
Where's the helicopter going?

73
00:05:23,967 --> 00:05:25,300
Conde and the rest are coming.

74
00:05:25,433 --> 00:05:27,300
They said they had something
important to say.

75
00:05:28,367 --> 00:05:29,500
About what, Chief?

76
00:05:29,633 --> 00:05:31,233
I don't know either.

77
00:05:31,367 --> 00:05:34,567
Conde, Dizon, Enriquez.

78
00:05:34,733 --> 00:05:35,800
What happened?

79
00:05:35,933 --> 00:05:39,867
Sir, maybe Enriquez and us
can talk privately first?

80
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:43,133
Noble, Robles.

81
00:05:45,367 --> 00:05:46,100
Sir.

82
00:05:54,933 --> 00:05:56,733
What's the important thing
you're going to say?

83
00:05:58,733 --> 00:06:00,333
Sir...

84
00:06:00,467 --> 00:06:02,133
they got Selena.

85
00:06:02,267 --> 00:06:03,500
What?

86
00:06:03,633 --> 00:06:04,767
How did that happen?

87
00:06:06,167 --> 00:06:09,333
Dizon and I don't know
how they got the address.

88
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:11,567
But I have a hunch
that Selena is right.

89
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:13,900
There's a spy here
at our station.

90
00:06:16,033 --> 00:06:17,467
What do you mean?

91
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,367
Is Amo involved in this?

92
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:21,667
Sir, if he's involved in this

93
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:25,133
that means he's part of the
human trafficking syndicate

94
00:06:25,267 --> 00:06:26,833
that kidnapped my godsister,

95
00:06:26,967 --> 00:06:28,633
Reign.

96
00:06:28,767 --> 00:06:29,900
Sir,

97
00:06:30,033 --> 00:06:32,733
we saw that Selena and Reign
were taken in a helicopter.

98
00:06:32,867 --> 00:06:34,900
Dizon, come with me.

99
00:06:35,033 --> 00:06:36,433
We'll talk to someone.

100
00:06:42,133 --> 00:06:43,667
Sir,

101
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:46,067
I know I'm not the only one
who's thinking about this.

102
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,200
Isn't it too much
of a coincidence?

103
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:50,300
Just when you were going
to ask Selena for a statement

104
00:06:50,433 --> 00:06:51,433
against Amo,

105
00:06:51,567 --> 00:06:53,500
the syndicate kidnapped her.

106
00:06:55,033 --> 00:06:56,567
I'll talk to Amo.

107
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:57,400
Wait.

108
00:07:00,167 --> 00:07:03,233
I will talk to him.

109
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:18,167
Tonyo...

110
00:07:26,533 --> 00:07:29,600
The star witness in the case
you're involved in

111
00:07:29,733 --> 00:07:31,467
was kidnapped earlier.

112
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:37,900
They were put on a plane
with some other women.

113
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,200
We don't know where
they're being taken.

114
00:07:42,333 --> 00:07:47,967
Do you think I'm involved
in a human trafficking activity?

115
00:07:51,967 --> 00:07:54,000
I don't know anything
about your star witness...

116
00:07:55,533 --> 00:07:58,733
but I hope you can save her.

117
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:08,833
Godfather,

118
00:08:08,967 --> 00:08:11,400
the helicopter we're looking
for landed on a private runway.

119
00:08:11,533 --> 00:08:14,233
Based on the CCTV footage,

120
00:08:14,367 --> 00:08:17,067
Reign and her companions were
transferred to another plane.

121
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:19,000
And wherever that plane lands,

122
00:08:19,133 --> 00:08:20,967
Lieutenant Conde and I
will go there.

123
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,000
Bobby...

124
00:08:24,533 --> 00:08:26,067
find Reign.

125
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:28,367
Please bring her back to me.

126
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:29,833
Bobby, please.

127
00:08:29,967 --> 00:08:33,100
Bobby, please bring Reign back
to me.

128
00:08:33,233 --> 00:08:34,733
Yes, Godfather.

129
00:08:34,867 --> 00:08:35,900
Yes, Godfather.

130
00:08:37,433 --> 00:08:38,600
Just a moment, Godfather.

131
00:08:42,133 --> 00:08:42,767
Hello?

132
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:44,267
Lieutenant Conde, any updates?

133
00:08:45,467 --> 00:08:46,700
Hello, Enriquez?

134
00:08:46,833 --> 00:08:48,600
The plane has landed.

135
00:08:48,733 --> 00:08:51,333
Chief is expediting our visas.

136
00:08:51,467 --> 00:08:52,400
Visa?

137
00:08:52,533 --> 00:08:54,333
Why? Where are we going?

138
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:56,267
Get ready.

139
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,267
We're flying to Dubai.

140
00:09:00,067 --> 00:09:01,833
What? Where did they take
my daughter?

141
00:09:01,967 --> 00:09:03,433
Godfather, she's in Dubai.

142
00:09:03,567 --> 00:09:04,200
Dubai?

143
00:09:05,567 --> 00:09:06,500
Why?

144
00:09:06,633 --> 00:09:09,100
Bobby, find Reign.
Bring her back.

145
00:09:09,233 --> 00:09:11,633
Godfather, I promise...

146
00:09:11,767 --> 00:09:14,400
I'll bring her back to you,
no matter what happens.

147
00:09:15,667 --> 00:09:18,300
- Please, okay? I'm begging you.
- Yes, Godfather.

148
00:09:25,267 --> 00:09:25,733
Sir.

149
00:09:28,633 --> 00:09:29,733
Here are your visas.

150
00:09:31,767 --> 00:09:33,867
I had to pull some strings

151
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:37,400
just to get these
on such short notice.

152
00:09:37,533 --> 00:09:39,267
That's why...

153
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,833
we have to make it count.

154
00:09:40,967 --> 00:09:43,133
Thank you, Sir,
for including me.

155
00:09:43,267 --> 00:09:44,767
It's supposed to be
just Conde and me...

156
00:09:45,867 --> 00:09:47,467
but he begged to include you.

157
00:09:51,933 --> 00:09:54,900
I know that Reign
is important to you.

158
00:09:55,033 --> 00:09:56,467
I just want to make it clear...

159
00:09:56,600 --> 00:10:00,000
our top priority is Selena.

160
00:10:01,333 --> 00:10:02,467
Understood?

161
00:10:02,867 --> 00:10:04,067
- Yes, Sir.
- Yes, Sir.

162
00:10:05,233 --> 00:10:06,200
Let's go.

163
00:10:14,267 --> 00:10:16,733
Welcome to Dubai,
Conde and Enriquez.

164
00:10:23,367 --> 00:10:24,467
Enriquez...

165
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,333
are you okay?

166
00:10:28,167 --> 00:10:30,333
I'm worried about Reign, Sir.

167
00:10:30,467 --> 00:10:33,733
I don't know how we're going
to find her here in Dubai.

168
00:10:33,867 --> 00:10:35,233
We don't know anything here.

169
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,800
Just trust me.

170
00:10:37,933 --> 00:10:40,100
We'll save your godsister.

171
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,233
Just to be clear...

172
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:46,333
Selena is our priority.

173
00:10:48,033 --> 00:10:49,933
But if we have to choose...

174
00:10:51,333 --> 00:10:52,667
between Reign and Selena...

175
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:54,400
We understand, Sir.

176
00:10:56,367 --> 00:10:57,300
Understood, Sir.

177
00:11:05,933 --> 00:11:07,000
Excuse me.

178
00:11:07,133 --> 00:11:08,200
Fellow Filipino,

179
00:11:08,367 --> 00:11:09,833
where is Burj Tu...

180
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,867
Oh my...

181
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,933
You're here?

182
00:11:15,933 --> 00:11:17,267
Enriquez!

183
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,167
Chief!

184
00:11:19,233 --> 00:11:20,633
What are you doing here?

185
00:11:20,767 --> 00:11:23,100
How about you? What are you
doing here in Dubai?

186
00:11:24,333 --> 00:11:26,100
Sir, you might have forgotten.

187
00:11:26,233 --> 00:11:27,967
I'm on vacation now.

188
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,067
How about you?

189
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,900
Are you three on vacation too?

190
00:11:31,033 --> 00:11:32,400
I didn't know that the three
of you were close.

191
00:11:32,533 --> 00:11:33,767
Work, Sir.

192
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,567
Selena was kidnapped.

193
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:37,100
We're investigating
something here.

194
00:11:38,167 --> 00:11:39,633
She was kidnapped
from the safehouse.

195
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:42,500
Selena was kidnapped?

196
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,767
This is a big case.

197
00:11:46,033 --> 00:11:49,333
Sir, if you need my service,
I'm willing to join you.

198
00:11:49,467 --> 00:11:50,533
Vacation with pay.

199
00:11:50,667 --> 00:11:51,567
No, Garcia.

200
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,333
This is an official mission.

201
00:11:54,467 --> 00:11:55,267
We can manage.

202
00:11:56,433 --> 00:11:57,833
But, Sir...

203
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,100
where are you staying?

204
00:12:01,633 --> 00:12:02,667
My batchmate...

205
00:12:04,133 --> 00:12:06,000
he is based here in Dubai,

206
00:12:06,133 --> 00:12:07,033
and he's a big shot.

207
00:12:07,167 --> 00:12:08,267
Is he a cop too, Sir?

208
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:10,500
He used to be a cop.

209
00:12:10,633 --> 00:12:13,600
You know, back when
we were students,

210
00:12:13,733 --> 00:12:14,767
he excels at so many things.

211
00:12:15,933 --> 00:12:18,400
He has a nice body
and he's handsome, too.

212
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,133
Probably even more so now.

213
00:12:21,267 --> 00:12:22,700
He's a big shot.

214
00:12:26,433 --> 00:12:27,967
He's here already.

215
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:29,100
Big shot.

216
00:12:29,233 --> 00:12:30,267
Nice car.

217
00:12:32,233 --> 00:12:33,200
Rudolf!

218
00:12:33,333 --> 00:12:34,067
Bok!

219
00:12:36,633 --> 00:12:37,967
Welcome to Dubai.

220
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,600
Thank you, Bok.

221
00:12:39,733 --> 00:12:40,767
Looking good.

222
00:12:40,900 --> 00:12:41,567
How are you?

223
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:42,667
I'm good.

224
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,433
Chief!

225
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:51,833
Chief, it looks like your friend
stood you up.

226
00:12:51,967 --> 00:12:53,200
There's no one inside.

227
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:54,700
He just sent his driver.

228
00:12:55,733 --> 00:12:58,133
This one talks too much.

229
00:12:59,533 --> 00:13:01,767
This is Lieutenant Conde.

230
00:13:04,367 --> 00:13:05,367
Sergeant Enriquez.

231
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:06,100
Sir.

232
00:13:07,167 --> 00:13:08,233
Lieutenant Garcia.

233
00:13:12,133 --> 00:13:13,967
He's my batchmate.

234
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:15,800
Captain Pong Marasigan.

235
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,700
He's the one you were talking
about earlier.

236
00:13:20,833 --> 00:13:22,100
Yes, he's the one.

237
00:13:22,267 --> 00:13:25,133
It seems like you only got
his name right.

238
00:13:25,267 --> 00:13:27,533
Sir, what happened?

239
00:13:27,667 --> 00:13:29,700
What do you mean
by what happened?

240
00:13:31,867 --> 00:13:33,233
If life is hard here in Dubai,

241
00:13:33,367 --> 00:13:35,167
you should have gone back
to the Philippines.

242
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:36,067
Garcia!

243
00:13:37,033 --> 00:13:38,833
Maybe you're overworked.

244
00:13:38,967 --> 00:13:39,567
Bok?

245
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:40,333
Bok...

246
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:44,533
I need your help.

247
00:13:59,533 --> 00:14:00,633
Have some tea first.

248
00:14:02,033 --> 00:14:03,000
Bok, thank you.

249
00:14:03,133 --> 00:14:04,133
Help yourselves.

250
00:14:06,033 --> 00:14:08,333
You know, in all my years
as an investigator,

251
00:14:08,467 --> 00:14:10,967
I've somehow built up a network.

252
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,367
By the way,

253
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:17,000
did you have any last leads
before you came here to Dubai?

254
00:14:17,133 --> 00:14:22,033
Names of the kidnappers,
identities of the kidnappers,

255
00:14:22,167 --> 00:14:23,367
or the syndicates?

256
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,667
Nothing, Sir.

257
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:28,733
All we know is the body number
of the helicopter they were on.

258
00:14:30,133 --> 00:14:32,333
Can we track that down, Sir?

259
00:14:32,467 --> 00:14:35,367
Okay, there's someone I can ask.

260
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,533
Just give me the body number,

261
00:14:37,667 --> 00:14:39,000
I'll take care of it.

262
00:14:39,133 --> 00:14:40,567
I'll just call him, okay?

263
00:14:43,933 --> 00:14:46,333
We'd better rest first.

264
00:14:46,467 --> 00:14:49,800
It's hard to move around
with jet lag.

265
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,833
Rest?

266
00:14:52,967 --> 00:14:55,900
Chief, is there nothing
we can do now?

267
00:14:56,033 --> 00:14:57,100
The longer it takes,

268
00:14:57,233 --> 00:15:00,133
the harder it will be
to find Selena and Reign.

269
00:15:00,267 --> 00:15:01,800
We know that, Enriquez.

270
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:06,233
But right now,
our resources are limited.

271
00:15:06,367 --> 00:15:08,833
Every lead we follow
must be right.

272
00:15:08,967 --> 00:15:10,367
We can't go wrong.

273
00:15:11,467 --> 00:15:12,933
Conde is right.

274
00:15:13,067 --> 00:15:14,367
Let's rest first.

275
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,600
First thing tomorrow,
we'll work on it.

276
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:31,733
This is Albert, the contact
I was telling you all about.

277
00:15:31,867 --> 00:15:33,067
Major Flores,

278
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:35,233
Lieutenant Conde,
and Sergeant Enriquez.

279
00:15:36,367 --> 00:15:36,933
Hi, Sir.

280
00:15:38,133 --> 00:15:42,033
Albert is a former PNP
who became a pimp.

281
00:15:42,167 --> 00:15:44,600
Boss, don't ruin my reputation.

282
00:15:44,733 --> 00:15:46,733
I thought this was
a birthday party,

283
00:15:46,867 --> 00:15:49,833
why are we with these policemen?

284
00:15:50,967 --> 00:15:52,233
I'll just go home.

285
00:15:52,367 --> 00:15:54,733
Come on, Albert.
Don't leave yet.

286
00:15:54,867 --> 00:15:57,800
They'll just ask you something.
Better yet, sit down.

287
00:15:57,933 --> 00:15:59,400
Sit down, just relax.

288
00:15:59,533 --> 00:16:03,433
Albert, we were just going
to ask about the women

289
00:16:03,567 --> 00:16:06,667
being brought here
from the Philippines.

290
00:16:07,933 --> 00:16:09,067
I don't know anything
about that.

291
00:16:09,233 --> 00:16:10,833
I've been out of that
for a year now.

292
00:16:10,967 --> 00:16:13,133
Albert, don't embarrass me.

293
00:16:13,267 --> 00:16:15,200
I told them I'd help them.

294
00:16:15,333 --> 00:16:16,767
Boss, I really don't know
anything about it.

295
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:22,067
Okay, I'll take care of this.
I'll just convince him.

296
00:16:32,667 --> 00:16:33,767
What?

297
00:16:33,900 --> 00:16:35,433
Do you know anything or not?

298
00:16:35,567 --> 00:16:38,767
Yes, I'm going to talk now.

299
00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:39,567
Yes.

300
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:43,433
You can proceed.
He's going to talk already.

301
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,067
Ask him.

302
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:47,933
Albert, do you have any idea
where those women

303
00:16:48,067 --> 00:16:49,567
you used to handle came from?

304
00:16:52,467 --> 00:16:54,967
Albert, they are asking you

305
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:58,033
if you have any idea
where those women you used

306
00:16:58,167 --> 00:16:59,500
to handle come from.

307
00:16:59,633 --> 00:17:00,233
Yes.

308
00:17:01,933 --> 00:17:03,600
They're the TNTs here,

309
00:17:03,733 --> 00:17:06,367
the ones who are in debt
and have done something wrong,

310
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:08,400
the ones who are desperate.

311
00:17:08,533 --> 00:17:10,167
That's what we're getting.

312
00:17:10,300 --> 00:17:12,633
Have you heard about those
who are being brought here

313
00:17:12,767 --> 00:17:14,300
and forced to work
against their will?

314
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:20,300
Albert, we just want to know
where our countrymen

315
00:17:20,433 --> 00:17:22,300
who are victims of human
trafficking are being taken.

316
00:17:23,633 --> 00:17:24,633
Help us.

317
00:17:24,767 --> 00:17:25,667
Yes.

318
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,367
I know something.

319
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:30,433
There is a building that is
being used as a dumping ground

320
00:17:30,567 --> 00:17:31,800
for women from the Philippines.

321
00:17:31,933 --> 00:17:33,033
Where is that building?

322
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:49,200
Bok, where is it?

323
00:17:49,333 --> 00:17:50,500
We are almost there
at the building

324
00:17:50,633 --> 00:17:52,033
that my contact mentioned.

325
00:17:52,167 --> 00:17:54,833
The women are being taken down
to the basement

326
00:17:54,967 --> 00:17:55,933
of that building.

327
00:17:56,067 --> 00:17:57,167
There is an entrance and exit

328
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:58,767
at the front and back
of the building.

329
00:17:58,900 --> 00:18:01,167
We need to cover the front
and back.

330
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:03,867
Enriquez, come with me.
Let's go to the front.

331
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,367
Conde, go check the back.

332
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:06,367
- Yes, Sir!
- Bok, how about me?

333
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:07,567
Bok...

334
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:08,567
stay here.

335
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:09,533
You're a civilian.
You can't be involved.

336
00:18:09,667 --> 00:18:11,333
Bok, my workout will just go
to waste.

337
00:18:12,467 --> 00:18:13,267
Bok!

338
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:15,333
I'm so ready!

339
00:18:15,467 --> 00:18:17,167
Please, Bok!

340
00:19:03,233 --> 00:19:03,867
Sir.

341
00:19:16,667 --> 00:19:18,067
Stop!

342
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,067
What are you doing here?

343
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:21,467
Who are you?

344
00:19:40,267 --> 00:19:41,300
Hey!

345
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:42,800
You're not allowed here.

346
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:43,667
Hey!

347
00:20:48,467 --> 00:20:50,100
Markus, we're under attack.

348
00:20:50,233 --> 00:20:50,833
What?

349
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,000
Get the girls now!

350
00:20:52,133 --> 00:20:53,367
Okay, okay.

351
00:21:07,300 --> 00:21:08,367
I want to go home!

352
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:09,133
Stop him!

353
00:21:09,300 --> 00:21:10,733
Let me go!

354
00:21:10,867 --> 00:21:12,233
Let's go!

355
00:21:12,367 --> 00:21:16,700
I want to go home.
I'm begging you. Let me go!

356
00:21:16,833 --> 00:21:19,000
- Let me go, please!
- Get in.

357
00:21:19,133 --> 00:21:20,900
I'm begging you, please.

358
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:45,000
He's still alive!

359
00:21:46,367 --> 00:21:47,633
Take them both!

360
00:21:49,467 --> 00:21:50,333
Mister.

361
00:22:02,633 --> 00:22:04,667
Where are you taking me?

362
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,567
Let me go!

363
00:22:08,933 --> 00:22:09,867
Selena!

364
00:22:11,333 --> 00:22:12,633
- Sir Tonyo?
- Hey!

365
00:23:12,933 --> 00:23:14,567
Selena?

366
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:15,633
Selena!

367
00:23:17,733 --> 00:23:18,933
Faster! Let's go!

368
00:23:45,033 --> 00:23:46,300
Where are the girls?

369
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,633
Where are the girls?

370
00:24:04,633 --> 00:24:07,100
Did you know that the police
officers we encountered

371
00:24:07,233 --> 00:24:09,600
at Selena's safehouse
followed us here in Dubai?

372
00:24:09,733 --> 00:24:10,867
Did they get Selena?

373
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:12,100
We're on our way to Milan.

374
00:24:12,233 --> 00:24:15,067
Find a way to solve this, Roman.

375
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:18,867
That means we won't have any
problems with Selena anymore.

376
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,667
Selena doesn't seem to know
anything, Boss.

377
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:22,267
Get that out of your mind.

378
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,433
First of all,

379
00:24:23,567 --> 00:24:24,800
Selena is already in the custody
of our people abroad.

380
00:24:24,933 --> 00:24:25,967
Selena sent a message!

381
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:26,800
What did she say?

382
00:24:26,933 --> 00:24:28,167
They'll bring us to Milan.

383
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:31,333
Conde, Garcia, Enriquez,
get Selena back.

384
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:32,333
Go to Milan.

385
00:24:32,467 --> 00:24:33,600
Beautiful!

386
00:24:34,633 --> 00:24:36,300
It's beautiful here, Bok.

387
00:24:36,433 --> 00:24:37,467
Don't worry.

388
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:41,367
We'll find Reign, Selena,
and the other girls, too.
